data.description: Introducing 3760 EATON GATE Lane, a captivating residence nestled in the heart of Auburn Hills, 48326. This meticulously maintained home seamlessly blends modern luxury with timeless charm. Boasting a spacious and open floor plan, this property offers an inviting atmosphere, perfect for both relaxation and entertainment. The kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring sleek countertops, high-end appliances, and ample cabinet space. The master suite is a sanctuary of comfort, complete with a spa-like ensuite bathroom and generous closet space. With three bedrooms and well-appointed living spaces, this home provides versatility for any lifestyle. The meticulously landscaped yard, coupled with a private backyard oasis, offers an ideal setting for outdoor gatherings. Conveniently located near amenities and major thoroughfares, this property provides easy access to the best that Auburn Hills has to offer. Don't miss the opportunity to make 3760 EATON GATE Lane your dream home. Schedule a showing today and experience the epitome of luxurious suburban living. Common area in subdivision includes tennis court, picnic gazebo, and pond. Pine Trace golf course within 1/2 mile. Entrance to I-75 just a mile South. **Avondale School District***
